{"tid":2428398,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁美芬倡就參選人資格設立「資格審查委員會」","createTime":"2021-03-01T13:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T05:42:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"99c91c2a0769581dd4073b47edd9061cbda8531a","tid":2428398,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:39:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578119-20210301.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578119-20210301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1x5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=8c0e8e74\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578119-20210301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7538fbc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578119-20210301.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中央有關部門在深圳舉辦第二日座談會，就完善香港選舉制度及落實「愛國者治港」原則，聽取香港各界人士意見。<br />\n<br />\n有份出席的基本法委員會委員梁美芬，在座談會後接受傳媒訪問時說，她一直倡議不應只由選舉主任去決定參選人的資格，認為要設立資格審查委員會，可減少以往很多的情況，例如很多人參選時簽署確認書，但當選進入區議會後所做的事，與提倡「港獨」及「自決」無異，這些情況就不理想，最好是一開始時就可做到資格審查。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬說，如果在各領域都能落實愛國者治港，香港會越來越好，將來亦可說服國家繼續實行一國兩制。"},{"pid":"b3f252d9ddb78851a1c80fca1a80e40b89b14798","tid":2428398,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dd2c577816f6e91c77a31dcca3f7464f05af00","tid":2428398,"uid":389053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:40:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdc66e26d6da533c52c586ba9d1e8ac243ca92db","tid":2428398,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:42:15.000Z","msg":"心繫加國"}]}